                    <br /><br />
                    - FlyWithLua is on your PC and you want to update?<br />
                    FlyWithLua can be updated in up to four simple steps:<br />
                    <i>
                        1) Make a backup of your files user.ini and user.exit if you have modified them. If not, just skip this step.<br />
                        2) Download this ZIP archive and extract it over your installation, to exchange every file with the new version.<br />
                        3) Delete the file "please read the manual.lua" inside the Scripts folder.<br />
                        4) Restore the files user.ini and user.exit (only if you have modified/backup them before).<br />
